Package org.odpi.openmetadata.fvt.opentypes.relationships.ForeignKey

Class ForeignKey

java.lang.Object
org.odpi.openmetadata.fvt.opentypes.common.Line
org.odpi.openmetadata.fvt.opentypes.common.OMRSLine
org.odpi.openmetadata.fvt.opentypes.relationships.ForeignKey.ForeignKey
All Implemented Interfaces:
Serializable
public class ForeignKey extends OMRSLine
ForeignKey is a relationships between an entity of type RelationalColumn and an entity of type RelationalColumn. The ends of the relationships are stored as entity proxies, where there is a 'proxy' name by which the entity type is known. The first entity proxy has primaryKey as the proxy name for entity type RelationalColumn. The second entity proxy has foreignKey as the proxy name for entity type RelationalColumn. Each entity proxy also stores the entities guid. The primary key for another column is stored in a relational column from another table to enable them to be joined.
